---
title: Italian Chicken & Roasted Roma Tomatoes with Mash & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Classic Italian flavours shine in this fuss-free feast. With herbed garlicky chicken, sweet bursts of roasted Roma tomatoes, creamy mash and a basil pesto dressing, it's enough to make even the most traditional Italian envious.
